The '''Cogennan Nothoiin''' were a sub-[[Species/Legends|species]] of the [[Nothoiin (species)/Legends|Nothoiin]]. Their culture especially developed the innate [[Pilot/Legends|piloting]] ability common to all Nothoiins, and so were known for their piloting savvy.

